cs.NI, cs.GT, cs.IT, cs.MM, cs.SY

This paper discusses the implementation of inter-operator device-to-device communication using spectrum sharing. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The paper also involves game theory and optimization, which suggests that it could belong to cs.GT (Computer Science and Game Theory) and cs.IT (Information Theory). Additionally, the paper mentions vehicular communication, which could place it in cs.MM (Multimedia) or cs.SY (Systems and Control).
